# Game Screen Requirements

This file documents the requirements for each screen in the "DestinyOath" (Xiantu Xuanfang) tower defense game as described in the [README.md](mdc:README.md).

## 1. Start Screen (StartScreen)
- Display game title "DestinyOath"
- Show background image
- "開始試煉" (Start Trial) button
- "玄境設定" (Settings) button

## 2. Game Screen (GameScreen)
- Display player's spirit power (靈力值) progress bar
- Show cultivation level (修為值)
- Display current trial/max trial (劫數/總劫數)
- Character displayed in center
- Show enemies and animations
- Display bullet firing animations
- Show enlightenment progress (悟道進度) bar
- "頓悟" (Enlightenment) button (available when progress is full)

## 3. Upgrade Screen (UpgradeScreen)
- Display "仙緣三擇" (Three Choices) title
- Show three upgrade option cards, each containing:
  - Icon
  - Name
  - Description
  - "擇此仙緣" (Choose This Destiny) button

## 4. Game Over Screen (GameOverScreen)
- Display "渡劫失敗" (Trial Failed) title
- Show final cultivation level
- Display highest trial reached
- "再入凡塵" (Try Again) button
- "返回仙山" (Return to Main Menu) button

The visual design for these screens should follow the prototype in [index.html](mdc:index.html) while implementing the screens according to the structure specified in the [app architecture](mdc:.cursor/rules/app-architecture.mdc).
